de.fraunhofer.fokus.oefit.adhoc.model.impl

Class AHOfferModelImpl

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.liferay.portal.model.impl.BaseModelImpl<AHOffer>
      • de.fraunhofer.fokus.oefit.adhoc.model.impl.AHOfferModelImpl
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    com.liferay.portal.model.BaseModel<AHOffer>, com.liferay.portal.model.ClassedModel, AHOfferModel, Serializable, Cloneable, Comparable<AHOffer>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    AHOfferBaseImpl

    public class AHOfferModelImpl
extends com.liferay.portal.model.impl.BaseModelImpl<AHOffer>
implements AHOfferModel
    The base model implementation for the AHOffer service. Represents a row in the "AHOFFER" database table, with each column mapped to a property of this class.

    This implementation and its corresponding interface AHOfferModel exist only as a container for the default property accessors generated by ServiceBuilder. Helper methods and all application logic should be put in AHOfferImpl.

    Author:
    Brian Wing Shun Chan
    See Also:
    AHOfferImpl, AHOffer, AHOfferModel, Serialized Form
